ygData.subject: Re: Lute of the Gypsy Princess?!
ygData.msgSnippet: I agree.  A particularly trusting Wizard (we had never met before) handed me one in Mistmoore and asked me to test it.  I found no difference in Healing rate
ygData.messageBody:
I agree. A particularly trusting Wizard (we had never met before) handed me one in Mistmoore and asked me to
test it. I found no difference in Healing rate between the Gypsy lute and a normal loot.

Kenross Cantoforjado, Level 24 Bard, Innoruuk
